# +----------------------------------------+
#
#     Rev: 2023-08-07
#  Inputs: $1=GUI
#    Uses: WEB_BROWSER_FOUND, WEB_BROWSER_APPS.
# Outputs: WEB_BROWSER, RUNAPP, ERROR.
#
# Summary: Detect web browser application.
#
